    <div class="main review-item" id="4958912">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4958912/" class="title-link">有些基础知识后，再去说欣赏吧。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4958912"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunqingxin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1216164-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunqingxin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小阿</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-05-22"
      class="main-meta">2011-05-22 16:54:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4958912_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  有一年去卢浮宫，专门请了博物馆里的华裔讲解员。一个青中年男子，获得了博物馆管理专业的博士学位。他一直眉头紧锁，看着宫中熙熙攘攘的游客。他厌恶游客们指手画脚，遛弯瞟着大师们的作品。他的介绍方法是在一个馆中选取一个作品，然后全情投入地讲作品的背景和精彩之处，说...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4958912/#comments">(10回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">41有用 / 2没用</span>
