  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6135790">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6135790/" class="title-link">我讨厌增订版</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6135790"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36687273/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36687273-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36687273/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">一品书堂</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-06-27"
      class="main-meta">2013-06-27 08:44:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6135790_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  艺术不分国界，为毛从台湾引进大陆还要搞神马增订版？！书后边，写替换图片达1/3，增删达1/8，而且现代艺术部分是他人写，蒋勋审定。唉，要一本原汁原味的怎么这么难？为什么又是增删，又是替换？！难怪越到后边我越不耐烦读下去，原来还有他人续写！还是想拥有蒋勋的原著。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6135790/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 1没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            湖南美术出版社2011版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6135790_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6135790_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7651786">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7651786/" class="title-link">通俗易懂，感受西方美术的魅力</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7651786"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/55335404/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u55335404-12.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55335404/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer"> 向沐然</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-11-07"
      class="main-meta">2015-11-07 15:47:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7651786_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   什么是美术？我看了一点的时候想，是否就是给我们带来美好的艺术。以前觉得美术就是画画，其实远不止如此，有些涂鸦画画很可能只是情绪的表达，简简单单的，没有那么多意义存在，倒知晓这也属于美术吧。看到最后，我想美术比原来以为得更加深沉，或许是存在于我们生命的一部分...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7651786/#comments">(3回应)</a>
